gredient> vnd mit <ingredient en="fig" commodity="Q2746643">veigen</ingredient> <ref target="">als czw dem <ingredient en="wafer" commodity="Q1226651" ana="comparison">obblaten</ingredient></ref></instruction> <instruction>wan dw die <dish en="pancake" commodity="Q44541">pletter</dish> gefult hast So mach ein <ingredient en="batter" commodity="Q29493">taig</ingredient> von <ingredient en="chicken egg" commodity="Q15260613">airen</ingredient></instruction> vnd <instruction>pachs dar Inne</instruction> vnd <servingTip>gibs haiß czw essen</servingTip> <closer>etc.</closer></div></body></text></TEI>